         Im pretty sure its not an exploit, been around forever and would be really easy for them to fix, if they chose to.</P><P>If you finish casting any spell less than 3 seconds after you finished casting the previous spell, you will get the Recovery Time Not Met message every time.  This is why when using a right click to refresh spell gems, you can get that message.  Happens with root, lich a lot. Any spell with a casting time under 3 seconds, you have to wait about a 2 count before casting if you are right clicking to refresh gems.</P><P>Vtyn</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
