         Noggin, anti gate spells (aka anchor spells) were supposed to be introduced with Luclin. The idea was wizzies could cast a spell that would prevent high level mobs from gating away when low on health, allowing them to be finished off. They were supposed to have had hideously long recast/refresh times (ie 30 secs) to balance out the power. Of course they were never introduced as Verant realised the exploit potential (one of which was just mentioned using the right click effect to cancel the wait timer)</P><P></P><P>Narben the Gnome Gnecro<BR>Colleague of Sanctuary<BR>Luclin server<BR>"Find your own damn witty comment"<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
